summary: ...DEPRESSION BECOMES TROPICAL STORM HENRIETTE... As of 11:00 AM HST Mon Aug 04 the center of Henriette was located near 14.8, -120.6 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
